ar parking Fee, Dry Laundry service and all other applicable charge if any. My apartment is suitable for Expats, especial it suites for a single person or a couple.</span>', 'Small corner life', 'The Pretty House (Serviced Apartment For Rent) located in The Premier, Ton That Thuyet Street, Cau Giay New Urban, the center of Cau Giay district which close to FPT university building, National university, Indochina tower, Cau Giay Business Center, International School, Keangnam Landmark Tower', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '163-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-11 18:18:59', '2018-03-11 11:18:59', '', 163, 'http://localhost/pretty-house/nha-lien-ke/163-revision-v1.html', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
